TEDTalks : What do consumers really want? - Joseph Pine (2004)

Customers want to feel what they buy is authentic, but &quot;Mass Customization&quot; author Joseph Pine says selling authenticity is tough because, well, there's no such thing. He talks about a few experiences that may be artificial but make millions anyway.
